data.text: The Round 22 edition will be on sale at all venues around the country. The Round 22 edition includes: Farewells to several retiring stars – North Melbourne teammates Jack Ziebell and Ben Cunnington, West Coast captain Luke Shuey, Richmond’s three-time premiership captain Trent Cotchin and Geelong and former Hawthorn premiership hero Isaac Smith. The Brownlow Medal has been thrown wide open after Collingwood young gun Nick Daicos was ruled out of the rest of the home and away season with a knee injury. LAURENCE ROSEN reports. The Round 22 edition will be on sale at all venues for $6.
